Class UDDIServiceCounter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.api.impl.UDDIServiceCounter

    public class UDDIServiceCounter
extends Object
implements DynamicMBean, Serializable
    This class provides MBean functionality that offers metrics on UDDI service method invocations and various management functions (documented by Alex O'Ree)

      • update

        public void update(UDDIQuery queryObject,
                   QueryStatus queryStatus,
                   long procTime)
        This updates the performance metrics for a given service. Note, as of jUDDI 3.2, procTime MUST be in milliseconds. Prior to 3.2 used nanoseconds
        Parameters:
        queryObject - the item that was executed
        queryStatus - success or fail status
        procTime - Expects time in milliseconds
